  "description": "A simple and relatively inexpensive full-size two-chamber household refrigerator with an exclusively classic set of functions and capabilities. The model was introduced to the market by the MPM brand in 2023. This is a two-door model with a total useful volume of 207 liters. The 69-liter freezer is located below. It has three containers with a transparent front wall, the minimum freezing temperature reaches -18 ° C. The cooling zone has 138 liters of free space and is equipped with three shelves, an additional pull-out container and three more door trays. LED backlighting is provided. The MPM 215-KB-39 refrigerator uses an automatic defrosting system. A traditional push-button control unit is used to set the cooling temperature. The compressor system makes noise at a level of no more than 40 W. The annual energy consumption of the model reaches 256 kW * h. If necessary, you can change the direction of the door leaves, you just need to rehang the hinges. The door leaf handles have a hidden design.",
